context: Following the defeat of the <b6_0>German<b6_0/> empire in <a0_0>World War I<a0_0/> and the abdication of the German Emperor, some revolutionary insurgents declared Alsace-Lorraine as an <a1_0>independent<a1_0/> Republic, without preliminary referendum or vote.
